  Locus:
    Page: 134
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Evil
---
In the eyes of God there is no evil. We suffer because of our ego. ...What,
after all, is right and wrong? That which takes you towards God is right
and that which takes you away from God is wrong. There is no question of
right and wrong for one who has realized God.
